	<item>
				<title>Sample Page</title>
		<link>http://themes.persitheme.com/yellowbird/color/sample-page/</link>
		<pubDate>Mon, 26 May 2014 11:17:30 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://themes.persitheme.com/yellowbird/color/?page_id=2</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

<blockquote>Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>

...or something like this:

<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>

As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://themes.persitheme.com/yellowbird/color/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!]]></content:encoded>

	<item>
				<title>shortcodes</title>
		<link>http://themes.persitheme.com/yellowbird/color/shortcodes/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2014 04:41:13 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://themes.persitheme.com/luckyblue/?page_id=5993</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[[column col="3/4"]

There are 30+ custom shortcodes available for create and design your pages. you can easily use shortcode and its properties only by 1 click on shortcode button in the bar on "edit post" or "edit page" when you use visual text editor.

[frame image="5998" width="870" height="435"]

As you can see in the picture, all shortcodes have properties that is useful for customize theme. all shortcodes come with whole properties and default values. you can ignore the properties with default value or without value, if you want.

[/column]]]></content:encoded>

[slider images="6346,6350,6347" width="300" height="170" effect="fold" align="right" showcontrol="off" showdirection="" showborder=""]
Vivamus pulvinar molestie sapien sit amet luctus. Nulla sagittis luctus tortor, eget eleifend lacus imperdiet ac. Sed vitae magna lectus. Mauris quam libero, pellentesque quis tristique eu, accumsan eu massa. Sed sed nulla nec ligula bibendum posuere vitae in risus. Vestibulum dolor libero, pharetra vehicula volutpat sit amet, ornare vitae purus. Suspendisse semper sagittis aliquet. Cras vel laoreet purus. Quisque ac tortor lectus, ac molestie elit. 		<content:encoded><![CDATA[This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

<blockquote>Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>

...or something like this:

<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>

As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://themes.persitheme.com/yellowbird/classic/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!]]></content:encoded>

Sed convallis massa eget metus vulputate ac tempus lectus mollis. ”]]></content:encoded>

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<strong class="dark-color">Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. When an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature.</strong>

It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.

Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source.]]></content:encoded>

	<item>
				<title>Contrary popular belief</title>
		<link>http://themes.persitheme.com/yellowbird/color/portfolio/contrary-popular-belief/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 05 Jul 2012 12:45:29 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://themes.persitheme.com/unique/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=301</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<strong class="dark-color">Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. When an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature.</strong>

It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.

Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source.]]></content:encoded>
